{
  "stem": "25773.6",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Masia, ?] I said-- oh yes, on their way to the trains, they stopped us.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And they took all of the men away to a church.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "All the men.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Stefan, and I-- we thought we'd never see him again.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "We thought they're going to burn them down in a church.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And then all the women and children boarded the train.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And we arrived at a place called Pruszkow, which again, was about half an hour away from Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And it was a detention camp.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "So we arrived there, and it was an enormous, enormous square.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And the end of the square was sort of barracks.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "It must have been, before the war, must've been the soldiers' barracks.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And-- and-- and there we went with masses of people.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "The floors, I remember, were very beautiful floors-- oak floors, but everything was slippery with food, and we had to queue for hours to get soup.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And the soup they gave us, very, very flat.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "Very flat plate, so when you-- they put the [INAUDIBLE], the soup on this, immediately it slipped over and you had nothing.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And we were slipping on this-- on this floor [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And full of vermin already, after a week, full of vermin.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And what was-- the procedure was like this.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "There were a lot of old and lot of lame people-- or people-- invalids.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "The-- the Polish nurses used to wait on the square while they were being discharged daily by the German command.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "They were-- they made this place-- especially because next to it was a big hospital.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "So all these people with-- unable to-- I mean, people-- invalids with-- and old were taken to this hospital by the Polish nurses, Red Cross nurses, and left there.",
      "word_count": 29
    }
  ],
